<h1><i class="fa fa-clock"></i>Customizing Your Desktop Clock</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/customizing-environment"><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Customizing Your Environment</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-clock"></i>Customizing Your Desktop Clock</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>Your <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> includes a clock application which is displayed in the <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> toolbar and allows you to view the time at a glace. </p>

	<div class="figure">
		<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/day-time.png" />
		<div class="caption">The Desktop Clock</div>
	</div>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-cog"></i>Clock Settings</h2>
			<p>The clock can be customized through the <a href="#apps/settings-manager">Settings Manager</a> app. To view and change the clock settings, click on the "Clock" tab. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/clock-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title='"Clock" Tab on the System Settings App'><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/clock-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">"Clock" Tab on the System Settings App</div>
			</div>

			<h2><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Clock Appearance</h2>
			<p>The clock's appearance is controlled using the <a href="#apps/theme-manager">Theme Manager</a> app.</p>
			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/clock-appearance.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title='"Clock" Tab on the Theme Manager App'><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/clock-appearance.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">"Clock" Tab on the Theme Manager App</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-clock"></i>Clock Configurations</h2>
			<p>A few example clock configurations: </p>

			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/day-date-time.png" />
					<div class="caption">Day + Date + Time</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/day-24-hr-time.png" />
					<div class="caption">Day + 24 HR Time</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/day-time-seconds.png" />
					<div class="caption">Day + Time + Seconds</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/day-date-time-seconds.png" />
					<div class="caption">Day + Date + Time + Seconds</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/led-display-light.png" />
					<div class="caption">LED Display (light)</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-clock/led-display-dark.png" />
					<div class="caption">LED Display (Dark)</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>